{"tid":1693466,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請老豆搵仔入一入嚟望望","createTime":"2019-11-04T15:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T15:29:27.000Z","uid":288036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b46629f423dc76bb46ed17d876ef97222774d0d6","tid":1693466,"uid":288036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"諗到個idea，想大家幫幫手比下意見<br />\n<br />\n我都知老豆搵仔好忙，希望可以睇下會唔會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地面對面打基本上唔夠警狗抽，想再喺心理上加多少少力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟睇過好基本既心理學，有theory 提過，「每個人做每一件事都有佢正面動機」。個「正面動機」係由嗰個人出發。而警狗既正面動機係驚比人清算，所以先發癲式搞手足（之前有post都有見過有人提及，少一個勇武，將來就死得冇咁慘）<br />\n<br />\n知道老豆搵仔有行動係警狗篤灰就冇事，個人認為可以加大力道，儲印花式篤灰，逐件事計，而唔係逐個人。比名比number ，篤夠5單，自爆自己所有罪行頂2單，入white list。比人篤到佢有而不報，踢出white list，想入翻就篤多3個，如此類推。至於White list點處置就由大家決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想話比mon post狗聽，唔洗驚，因為我地一定會贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小小意見，唔知有冇用，大家一齊brainstorm 下。求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9e012b2e889ff83f497aedbc4947f7c6efc71f5","tid":1693466,"uid":288036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"冇力推求幫推"},{"pid":"14317378decc0c5bf5512eddb0fa01eb0806b698","tid":1693466,"uid":288036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"冇力推求幫推"}]}